Replication for node-webkit issue #809 
https://github.com/rogerwang/node-webkit/issues/809

Steps:

1. Go to the testserver directory.

2. Start the little webserver:
    node testserver.js

3. Go to a different terminal.

4. Go to the testapp directory.

5. Run the node-webkit app here:
    nw .

6. After the apps start, click on the "Open pop up" button.

7. A pop up will open. Open the dev-tools using the toolbar.

Result: The console in the dev-tools shows the error:


Tested with node-webkit-v0.9.2-linux-x64, on Kubuntu 13.10 64bit 

